creator: Modo Labs, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
To use Modo Campus, you must have an existing Modo application and Campus code. Please contact Modo to obtain your institution’s Campus code.

Trusted by hundreds of companies, institutions and hospitals in over 30 countries, Modo Labs offers an enterprise-scale mobile engagement and communication platform that allows customers to quickly and easily create institutional or corporate apps that engage recruits, employees, candidates, students, faculty, and alumni. By using Modo, our customers quickly unlock innovation and digitally transform their organizations, by harnessing the domain skills of any person in their Company or University, no matter their technical skill set.
